ZH: 我常常忘了带钥匙。
EN: I often forget to bring my keys.
ZH: 她忘了今天是你的生日。
EN: She forgot that today is your birthday.
ZH: 他忘了回复我的短信。
EN: He forgot to reply to my message.
ZH: 我忘了关灯。
EN: I forgot to turn off the lights.
ZH: 她忘了在炉子上放东西。
EN: She forgot to put something on the stove.
ZH: 你忘了拿手机了。
EN: You forgot to bring your phone.
ZH: 我们忘了提前预订餐厅。
EN: We forgot to make a reservation at the restaurant.
ZH: 他们忘了去火车站接我。
EN: They forgot to pick me up from the train station.
ZH: 我忙得忘了吃午饭。
EN: I was so busy that I forgot to eat lunch.
ZH: 老师忘了布置作业。
EN: The teacher forgot to assign homework.
ZH: 我总是忘了密码。
EN: I always forget my password.
ZH: 我忘了这个单词的意思。
EN: I forgot the meaning of this word.
ZH: 她忘了告诉我今晚有聚餐。
EN: She forgot to tell me about the dinner party tonight.
ZH: 我忘了明天有个会议。
EN: I forgot about the meeting tomorrow.
ZH: 他们忘了今天晚上有演出。
EN: They forgot about the performance tonight.
ZH: 我们时常忘了锁门。
EN: We often forget to lock the door.
ZH: 她忘了给我回电话。
EN: She forgot to call me back.
ZH: 他忘了在哪里放车钥匙了。
EN: He forgot where he put the car keys.
ZH: 我忘了你的生日派对在哪里。
EN: I forgot where your birthday party will be held.
ZH: 我们忘了明天是假日。
EN: We forgot that tomorrow is a holiday.
